The '''Half Transmogrified Junction''' is as it's name suggests, half of a [[Main/en/Transmogrified]] Junction.

[[File:en/Ttd.half.transmogrified.variant.png|frame|none|Half Transmogrified Junction with bridges]]

===Pros===
*Quite fast.
*Quite compact.
*Traffic jams are unlikely since tracks split before they merge.
*No loops.

===Cons===
*The slopes makes some trains go slower. 

